Prophet Muhammad ﷺ.­

🌙 Nabi Muhammad ﷺ ki Family (Khandan ke Naam)
👨 Walid (Father)
    • Hazrat Abdullah ibn Abdul Muttalib (RA)
👉 Nabi ﷺ ke walid, jo aapke paidaish se pehle hi wafat kar gaye.
👩 Walida (Mother)
    • Hazrat Amina bint Wahb (RA)
👉 Nabi ﷺ ki walida, jo jab aap 6 saal ke the, wafat kar gayin.
👴 Dada (Grandfather)
    • Hazrat Abdul Muttalib (RA)
👉 Quraysh ke leader, Ka’aba ke muhtamim. Aap ne Nabi ﷺ ki kafi hifazat ki.
👨‍🦱 Chacha (Uncles) – Abdul Muttalib ke bete
    • Hazrat Abu Talib → Nabi ﷺ ki kafi hifazat ki, lekin iman nahi laye.
    • Hazrat Abbas (RA) → Baad mein Islam qabool kiya.
    • Hazrat Hamza (RA) → Islam ke bohot bare supporter, “Sayyid-ush-Shuhada”.
    • Abu Lahab → Islam ke dushman, Qur’an mein bhi zikr.
👩 Pehli Biwi
    • Hazrat Khadija (RA)
👉 Nabi ﷺ ki pehli aur azeem biwi, jo sabse pehle Islam lai.
🧒 Bache (Children)
    • Qasim (RA) → bachpan mein wafat.
    • Zainab (RA)
    • Ruqayyah (RA)
    • Umm Kulthum (RA)
    • Fatimah (RA) → sabse mashhoor beti, Hazrat Ali (RA) ki biwi.
    • Abdullah (RA) → bachpan mein wafat.
    • Ibrahim (RA) → Madina mein paida hue, bachpan mein wafat.

🌸 Teaching Tip for GIO Class:
    • Aap isay “Family Tree Chart” bana kar dikhaiye (Father → Mother → Dada → Uncles → Wives → Children).
    • Quiz mein simple sawal puchhiye jaise:
        ◦ Nabi ﷺ ki walida ka kya naam tha?
        ◦ Kaunse chacha Islam ke dushman the?
        ◦ Nabi ﷺ ki sabse mashhoor beti kaun thi?

🌙 Story 1: Paidaish-e-Rasool ﷺ 
Makkah ek purane sheher tha jahan log apne baap dada ke deen, but-parasti (idols worship) mein gumrah the. Lekin Allah Ta’ala ne poori insaniyat ki hidayat ke liye apne Aakhri Nabi ko yahan bhejna tha.
Rasool Allah ﷺ ka paidaish Aam-ul-Fil (Hathi wale saal) mein hua, jab Yemen ka hukmaran Abrahah ne apni fauj ke sath Ka’aba girane ki koshish ki. Lekin Allah ne unko choti choti parindon (Ababeel) se halak kar diya.
Isi saal, 12 Rabi-ul-Awwal ke din, Hazrat Amina (RA) ke ghar mein Nabi Muhammad ﷺ paida hue. Aapke walid Hazrat Abdullah (RA) pehle hi wafat pa chuke the, aur walida Hazrat Amina ne aapko bacha ke taur par pala.
Bachpan mein, aapko pehle Halima Sa’dia (RA) ke sath rehnay ke liye diya gaya jo ek doodh pilane wali (foster mother) thi. Allah ne unke ghar mein barkat daal di, aur chhote se gaon mein bhi har cheez bhar gayi.
📝 Quiz with Answers (Story 1)
Q1. Nabi ﷺ ki paidaish kis saal hui?
👉 Jawab: Aam-ul-Fil (Hathi wala saal) mein.
Q2. Abrahah kis cheez ko girana chahata tha?
👉 Jawab: Ka’aba ko.
Q3. Allah ne Abrahah ki fauj kaise tabah ki?
👉 Jawab: Ababeel parindon ke zariye, jo chhoti chhoti pathriyan lekar aaye aur fauj ko tabaah kar diya.
Q4. Nabi ﷺ ka paidaish kis mahine aur tareekh ko hui?
👉 Jawab: 12 Rabi-ul-Awwal ko.
Q5. Aapke walid ka kya naam tha? Aur kya paidaish ke waqt zinda the?
👉 Jawab: Walid ka naam Hazrat Abdullah (RA) tha, aur aap ﷺ ke paidaish se pehle wafat ho chuke the.
Q6. Aapko doodh pilane wali ka kya naam tha?
👉 Jawab: Hazrat Halima Sa’dia (RA).

🌙 Story 2: Bachpan ke Waqiyat — Halima Sa’dia ke Ghar Barkat & Shiq-e-Sadr
Paidaish ke baad, Nabi ﷺ ko Arab ki riwayat ke mutabiq gaon mein doodh pilane wali aurat ke sath bheja gaya. Allah ki marzi se, aap ﷺ ka doodh pilane wali Hazrat Halima Sa’dia (RA) bani.
Jab Halima (RA) ne Nabi ﷺ ko apne sath liya, us waqt unka ghar bohot ghurbat mein tha. Unki sawari kamzor thi, doodh kam hota tha, aur ghar mein tangi thi. Lekin jaise hi unhone Nabi ﷺ ko apne sath liya, Allah ne unke ghar mein barkat daal di:
    • Unki sawari tez ho gayi,
      Halima Sa’dia (RA) jab Nabi ﷺ ko le kar apne gaon wapas gayin, to unki gadha sawari (jo pehle bohot kamzor aur dheemi chalti thi) achanak bohot tez aur taaqatwar ho gayi.
    • Doodh barh gaya,
    • Ghar mein sabko sukoon aur sukh milne laga.
Yeh sab Allah ki qudrat thi, jo apne Aakhri Nabi ﷺ ke wujood ki barkat thi.
Bachpan mein ek aur waqiya hua: Shiq-e-Sadr (Seena Cheerna). Ek din Nabi ﷺ Halima (RA) ke bete ke sath kheltay hue the. Do farishte aaye, unhone Nabi ﷺ ka seena khola, usme se ek chhota sa kaala daagh nikal kar phenk diya, aur phir seena band kar diya.
Halima (RA) aur unke shauhar ghabra gaye, lekin ye Allah ka mojza tha — is waqiya ka maqsad tha Nabi ﷺ ke dil ko paak karna aur tayyar karna risalat ke liye.
.

📝 Quiz with Answers (Story 2)
Q1. Nabi ﷺ ka doodh pilane wali ka kya naam tha?
👉 Jawab: Hazrat Halima Sa’dia (RA).
Q2. Jab Halima ne Nabi ﷺ ko apne sath liya, unke ghar mein kya tabdeeli aayi?
👉 Jawab: Ghar mein barkat aa gayi — doodh barh gaya, sawari tez ho gayi, sukoon mil gaya.
Q3. Shiq-e-Sadr ka waqiya kya hai?
👉 Jawab: Do farishton ne Nabi ﷺ ka seena cheera, ek chhota sa kaala daagh nikal diya, aur phir seena band kar diya.
Q4. Is waqiya ka maqsad kya tha?
👉 Jawab: Nabi ﷺ ke dil ko paak karna aur risalat ke liye tayyar karna.
Q5. Shiq-e-Sadr ke waqt Nabi ﷺ kahan aur kis ke sath the?
👉 Jawab: Apne doodh bhai (Halima Sa’dia ke bete) ke sath kheltay the.
